line_1: Just guardian of those laws thy voice explain'd,
line_2: And meriting all titles thou hast gain'd —

line_1: May the soft Riddle never be explain'd,
line_2: Lest the neglected blush to be disdain'd;
And all her Contradictions so maintain'd.

line_1: And thus the meaning smile explain'd.
Are by those charming Orators explain'd.
